    #-You walk down the hallway before bumping into a chill looking girl-
    show pov shocked_talk at left
    with dissolve
    show zar shocked at right
    with dissolve
    pov "Oh! I am so sorry!"
    show pov embarrassed at left
    show zar embarrassed_talk at right
    zar "No, no. Don't worry about it, I- *Yawn* I don't have the best reflexes this time a day either."
