    zar "I think I haven’t seen you before but my brain plays tricks on me at this hour so I better ask."
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show zar neutral at right
    pov "Fair enough."
    pov "Yeah, I am the new kid. My name is [povname]. And yours?"
    show pov neutral at left
    show zar neutral_talk at right
    zar "Zariah. Nice to see a new face in town."
    zar "How are you liking it so far?"
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show zar neutral at right
    pov "It's a nice place."
    show pov embarrassed_talk at left
    show zar embarrassed at right
    pov "Hey, um… Sorry, I don't mean to come off as rude, but are you okay? You look like you are about to fall over any second now."
    show pov neutral at left
    show zar bored_talk at right
    zar "Heh, don't worry about it, I get that a lot."
    zar "I work the night shift, so it's normal for me to have rough mornings when things go wild at night."
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show zar bored at right
    pov "You in the club business?"
    show pov neutral at left
    show zar neutral_talk at right
    zar "Impressive!"
    zar "How could you tell?"
    show pov smirk_talk at left
    show zar neutral at right
