    show pov neutral at left
    show zar neutral_talk at right
    zar "Not bad there, new kid!"
    zar "You know a lot about audio equipment?"
    show pov bored_talk at left
    show zar bored at right
    pov "I had a tech phase, back in the day."
    pov "Saved, an entire month, to get some 'Bases' by Dr. Drae."
    pov "Watched them all in MeTube; UrAvgCustomer, Marques Brownly, LionelsTechTricks, Lazy Gear Reviews."
    show pov bored at left
    show zar bored_talk at right
    zar "Gotta start somewhere, right?"
    zar "What did you listen to back then?"
    show pov bored_talk at left
    show zar bored at right
    pov "Mostly things like Antarctic Apes, BD-NY and Deaf Bunk. I've been trying to broaden my musical horizons since then."
    show pov bored at left
    show zar bored_talk at right
    zar "Nothing wrong with the classics."
    zar "Say, do you happen to like EDM?"
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show zar neutral at right
    pov "I keep an open mind."
    pov "Music is meant to be heard, so might as well listen to as much as you can, right?"
    show pov neutral at left
    show zar neutral_talk at right
    zar "Oh, you and I are going to get along fabulously."
    show pov confused at left
    show zar bored_talk at right
    zar "Have you ever heard of the indie artist ‘Karma’?"
    show pov confused_talk at left
    show zar bored at right
    pov "I am pretty new to the EDM genre so I can't say I do."
    show pov bored at left
    show zar bored_talk at right
    zar "Whip your phone out. Read this code for her playlist."
    zar "Give a listen and tell me what you think."
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show zar neutral at right
    pov "Hey, isn't this… You?"
    show pov neutral at left
    show zar neutral_talk at right
    zar "Heh, guilty as charged."
    zar "I play at the club every night with the weekends being my busiest moments."
    show pov neutral_talk at left
    show zar neutral at right
    pov "Wow!"
    pov "You should have told me I was talking to a star!"
    pov "I would have at least made a deeper voice or something."
    show pov smirk at left
    show zar smirk_talk at right
    zar "Hehe, the way you do now is just fine by me."
    zar "Come see me play sometime, I'll be sure to dedicate you a song if I see you among the crowd."
    show pov smirk_talk at left
    show zar smirk at right
    pov "Mind signing something for me? I want to be able to tell people and have proof I met the famous \"Karma\" before she hit it big and became a superstar."
    show pov embarrassed at left
    show zar smirk_talk at right
    zar "Heh, alright. Fine, but only because you are cute."
